{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 356.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Rouf ?] was going to raise some money from a friend of his who was a banker in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we-- we were both getting out of the Navy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew we were going to get out of the Navy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, well, I got down to-- finally got to the place where these FSes were supposed to be held-- managed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found out that I had been beaten by one day by, guess whom?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Moran Shipping and Tugboats from New York City.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had them all, and were reselling them at about four or five times the price and I-- we couldn't afford them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was feeling really down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I called up [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rouf ?] in San Francisco, and I said, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rouf, ?] I said, I'm sorry, but this isn't going to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We can't get the ships.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he says, well, I got news for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't get the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were feeling real down in the mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went around to the Mayflower Hotel on Connecticut Avenue and I was having a few drinks and feeling sorry for myself, and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I happened to be talking to some Army major.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were weeping on each other's shoulders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I mentioned somehow that I could speak German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, why don't you go to Nuremberg?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, what the hell is at Nuremberg?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, don't you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're going to try these war criminals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First I'd heard of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I'd been out in the Pacific.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, yeah, there's some colonel over in the-- in the Pentagon that's hiring people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name is Dostert.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, well, I was supposed to be at the Pentagon the next day anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
